Company Overview of Wolverine Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Wolverine Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to corporations. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investments markets across the globe. It employs a structural arbitrage strategy as a hedging technique while making its investments. The firm also uses credit arbitrage, risk arbitrage, and options strategies to construct its investment portfolios. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to make its investments. The firm conducts in-house research to support its investments. Wolverine Asset Management, LLC was founded in 20...
Wolverine Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to corporations. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investments markets across the globe. It employs a structural arbitrage strategy as a hedging technique while making its investments. The firm also uses credit arbitrage, risk arbitrage, and options strategies to construct its investment portfolios. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to make its investments. The firm conducts in-house research to support its investments. Wolverine Asset Management, LLC was founded in 2001 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with an additional offices in New York City and London, United Kingdom.
